'''德西'''（'''Dessie'''、'''Dese'''或'''Dessye'''）是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]中北部[[阿姆哈拉州|阿姆哈拉州]][[南沃洛地區|南沃洛地區]]的小鎮，座標{{Coord|11|8|N|39|38|E}}，海拔2,470米至2,550米。鎮內有電力供應、電話和郵政服務。根據[[埃塞俄比亞中央統計局|埃塞俄比亞中央統計局]]2005年的資料，德西人口約169,104，其中男性86,167人，女性82,937人。<ref>[http://www.csa.gov.et/text_files/2005_national_statistics.htm CSA 2005 National Statistics] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061123121716/http://www.csa.gov.et/text_files/2005_national_statistics.htm |date=2006-11-23 }}, Table B.4</ref>

2021年10月30日，埃塞俄比亞軍[[提格雷戰爭|撤出]]德西。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/10/30/ethiopias-tigray-rebels-say-captured-strategic-town-of-dessie |title=Ethiopia’s strategic town of Dessie ‘captured’ by rebel forces |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-10-30 |accessdate=2021-11-01 |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216020219/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/10/30/ethiopias-tigray-rebels-say-captured-strategic-town-of-dessie }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.dailysabah.com/world/africa/ethiopian-army-launches-new-offensive-to-capture-dessie |title=Ethiopian army launches new offensive to capture Dessie |work=Daily Sabah |date=2021-10-31 |accessdate=2021-11-01 |archive-date=2021-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105104722/https://www.dailysabah.com/world/africa/ethiopian-army-launches-new-offensive-to-capture-dessie }}</ref>同年12月6日，埃塞俄比亞政府宣佈軍隊已收復德西。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/6/ethiopia-recapture-dessie-kombolcha-tigrayan-rebels |title=Ethiopian forces recapture two key towns from Tigrayan forces |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-12-06 |accessdate=2021-12-09 |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216020327/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/6/ethiopia-recapture-dessie-kombolcha-tigrayan-rebels }}</ref>

